Some values (ordered) to give an impression:

                   0                  -- just 0
        -1/2                1/2       -- l 0 = -1/2 and r 0 = 1/2
   -3/4      -1/4      1/4       3/4  -- l (l 0), l (r 0), r (l 0) and r (r 0)

